<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 68. Clubiona spp. of the C. filicata group, male palp, retrolateral view A C. reichlini B C. filicata C C. banna sp. nov., holotype. Abbreviations: C = conductor; E = embolus; TA = tegular apophysis; RTA = retrolateral tibial apophysis. Scale bars: 0.1 mm." , "Figure 58. Clubiona spp. of the C. filicata group, male palp, ventral view A C. reichlini B C. filicata C C. banna sp. nov., holotype. Abbreviations: C = conductor; E = embolus; EB = embolar base; TA = tegular apophysis; RTA = retrolateral tibial apophysis. Scale bars: 0.1 mm." , "Figure 39. Male habitus of Clubiona filicata A dorsal view B ventral view C lateral view. Scale bar: 1 mm (equal for A-C)." , "Figure 38. Male palp of Clubiona filicata A prolateral view B retrolateral view C bulb, prolateral view D bulb, ventral view E bulb, retrolateral view. Abbreviations: E = embolus; EB = embolar base; RTA = retrolateral tibial apophysis; TA = tegular hump. Scale bars: 0.1 mm (equal for A, B, equal for C-E)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/535477" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/535467" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/535448" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/535447" .

